    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>BridgeDegree collects and uses your information to provide the programme, match you with mentors and placements, and maintain your Career Passport. We do not sell your data. We share information only where necessary for verification (e.g. employers verifying credentials) or with your consent.</p>
    <p>You can request access to or deletion of your data by contacting us at info@bridgedegree.com.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="policy-section" style="background: var(--surface-2);">
