    <h2>Terms of use</h2>
    <p>By using BridgeDegree you agree to use the platform for its intended purpose — building and verifying your career credentials — and to provide accurate information in applications and placements. Misrepresentation may result in removal from the programme and revocation of credentials.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="policy-section">
